From 9093320c3802eefbe9853d53f8b067349825c0cc Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mohd Ayaan Anwar <mohd.anwar@oss.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 30 Mar 2026 01:22:34 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 05/12] net: ethernet: tc956x: Update EEE API to use
 ethtool_keee (kernel 6.9)

struct ethtool_eee was renamed to struct ethtool_keee in kernel 6.9 and
the bitmap fields changed from u32 to link-mode bitmaps.  Update all
EEE-related functions to use the new struct, replace
ethtool_convert_link_mode_to_legacy_u32() with linkmode_copy() for the
get path, and replace phydev->eee_broken_modes with
phydev->eee_disabled_modes.

Upstream-Status: Submitted [https://github.com/TC956X/TC9564_Host_Driver/pull/4]
Signed-off-by: Mohd Ayaan Anwar <mohd.anwar@oss.qualcomm.com>
---
